Review:
I think Dokja's biggest weakness is his half hearted belief that his protective instincts are a negative survival trait. But the only reason we're around as a species is due to our ability to work together. The fable of the one true hero is mostly that and even in those stories there are almost always others who sacrifice themselves to get the "Chosen One" where they need to be.Or if if you want the sayin;
"Know one is an island."
/Shrug.
